# Narratoria

A work in progress app for an AI-backed narrative driven storyteller and game master.

## Dart+Flutter Rich Desktop App with Agent Skills

This branch explores using Dart and Flutter to build a crossplatform rich desktop app that leverages agents with skills and CLI tools to execute workflows for the narrator AI.

## Quick Start

### Development

```bash
# From project root
./run-dev.sh
```

### Building Release

```bash
# From project root
./build-macos.sh
```

### Running Tests

```bash
cd src
flutter test
```

